content.rendered:
Directed by Anubhuti Kashyap

Written by Saurabh Bharat. Saurabh Bharat. Anubhuti Kashyap. Sumit Saxena. Sumit Saxena. Vishal Wagh

Star Rakul Preet Singh(Dr Fatima Siddiqui). Ayushmann Khurrana(Dr Uday Gupta (Guddu)). Shefali Shah(Dr Nandini Shrivastav). Sheeba Chaddha(Shobha Gupta). Ayesha Kaduskar(Kavya). Abhinay Raj Singh(Sheru). Indraneil Sengupta(Dr. Ashok Gupta). Paresh Pahuja(Arif). Jhumma Mitra(Dr. Madhavi Gosain). Karishma Singh(Dr. Ruchi). Anju Gaur(Pushpa Gaur (Boski)). Abhay Mishra(Chaddha). Shraddha Jain(KLPD (Dr Kumudhlata Pamulparthi Diwakaran)). Priyam Saha(Dr. Jenny Jacob). Raj Sharma(Vinod kumar jaiswal). Azzy Bagria(Doctor (as Bagria Azzy)).Satendra Soni. Akash Sinha(Jagdish Sahay). Sharvari Deshpande(Priyanka Singh). Devas Dixit(Pappu Sahu). Pooja Sarup(Nurse Sunita). Anshumaan Srivastava(Ward Boy)

Language Hindi

Producers Zaid Ali. Zohaib Ali. Alex Anthony Fernandes. Vineet Jain. Amrita Pandey. Yogiraj Shetty

Production Junglee Pictures
